Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(OP)
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとうの言葉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,木漏れ日みたいで、いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,空 雲 果てしない道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ちっちゃい存在同士 手を取り
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,もっと 壮大 夢見てもいいかい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なんて 寛大な 地球だい？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,そう、きっと特別な双眼鏡だって、ね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,探した景色は見つからない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,世界で一番の絶景ポイントは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,いつも目の前の「その笑顔」だったから
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,ありがとう いつもとなりにいてくれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,それだけでもう何もいらなかったよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,なかなか素直に言えないこの気持ちあふれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今日もコハルビヨリだ いいね♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:04.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,一句「謝謝你」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.11,0:00:10.70,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就像掠過樹梢的陽光 讚♪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:25.76,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,藍天 白雲 漫漫長路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.34,0:00:31.09,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,同樣渺小的存在 只要手牽著手
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.39,0:00:35.99,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就能心懷更壯大的夢想？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.38,0:00:40.92,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,地球多麼寬大
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.13,0:00:46.00,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 就算特製的望遠鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:50.87,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,也找不到心中的景色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:55.50,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,因為世界上最棒的景點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.71,0:01:03.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,就是時刻綻放在眼前的那份笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:08.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你陪伴我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.37,0:01:13.16,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,有你相伴 別無所求
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.34,0:01:19.08,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿心中的這份心情 總是說不出口
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.15,0:01:24.64,OP,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也是暖和的小陽春 讚♪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.97,0:01:29.68,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,0)}翻譯：dgwxx／其他：cunhan
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,(main)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.82,0:01:34.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶油蛋糕？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.61,0:01:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有沒有什麼能做好的秘訣 能教教我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.70,0:01:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是呢 最重要的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.71,0:01:42.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最重要的…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.43,0:01:44.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是愛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.61,0:01:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有…稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.25,0:01:50.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這是我家的配方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs35}巧克力奶油蛋糕的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}材料
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,低筋麵粉 120g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,可可粉   12g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,泡打粉   一小勺
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,砂糖     100g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,無鹽奶油  100g
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,雞蛋     中號大小的2個
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力   適量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,牛奶     適量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs30}工具
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:51.04,recipe,NTP,0,0,0,,蛋糕模具 量勺 篩子\N臉盆 打泡器 橡膠鏟
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:00.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.37,0:01:53.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍徵調整一下配方 在家裡也能做出來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:55.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先照這個做看看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.20,0:01:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝店長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.19,0:01:59.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道能不能做好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.93,0:02:03.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒問題 做點心就像做數學一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.79,0:02:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要正確掌握材料份量 按照規定步驟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.24,0:02:11.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定會得到相同的結果 相同的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.89,0:02:13.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後就是愛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.71,0:02:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡一邊想著吃蛋糕的人一邊做
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.96,0:02:18.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.21,0:02:19.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.39,0:02:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵要烤蛋糕？好厲害啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:25.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想明天爬山的時候帶去吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看不出小葵還喜歡戶外活動呢 好帥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:31.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.73,0:02:32.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟男朋友去？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.16,0:02:35.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.85,0:02:37.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有女生啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.24,0:02:38.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.99,0:02:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小葵這麼可愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.45,0:02:43.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路上當心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.19,0:02:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.94,0:02:46.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會買伴手禮回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.61,0:02:50.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的？謝謝小葵 小光好高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:58.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:03:02.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心裡想著吃蛋糕的人高興的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.91,0:03:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,的確 就算吃蛋糕的人是日向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.89,0:03:10.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帶著一臉滿足的表情來吃的話…心裡還是有點高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.62,0:03:16.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好！加油做出充滿愛情的蛋糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.15,0:03:22.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,儘管有不少插曲 明天終於要和日向履約去爬谷川岳了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.12,0:03:25.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有小楓學姐和可可娜醬
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:30.27,title,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜的飯能大冒險
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜：
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,提前一天祝你生日快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs36}Happy Birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚一起慶祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.36,note,NTP,100,0,0,,by 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.99,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雨衣和替換的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.69,0:03:37.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水和零食
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.40,0:03:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備完成
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.81,0:03:42.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 再拿一條毛巾去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.21,0:03:56.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是…生日禮物？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.79,0:04:00.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還不能打開吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.11,0:04:06.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要…打開了！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.35,0:04:11.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之前說過想要登山靴來著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽還記著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.64,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸剛好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.71,0:04:52.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出去…吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:57.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.82,0:05:14.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去爬天覽山吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.22,0:05:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然…對了！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去那裡看看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.06,0:06:20.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.61,0:06:23.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.12,0:06:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請收下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.60,0:06:30.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牠也讓你收下呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.65,0:06:36.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.65,0:06:39.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.93,0:07:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.01,0:07:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幾年沒來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:37.11,yama_neta,NTP,0,0,0,,飯能市曙光兒童森林公園 位於飯能市政府附近 因高度重現了芬蘭卡通姆明（Moomins）的世界而著名
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.85,0:08:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的彷彿置身於故事的世界一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.05,0:08:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢～馬～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.44,0:08:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡 或許還真的有妖精呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.57,0:08:50.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.11,0:09:07.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽好晚…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.80,0:09:43.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢馬
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:45.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.96,0:09:46.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.73,0:09:51.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:53.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起 太晚回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:10:00.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天去谷川岳吧 所以想今天幫你慶生呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.06,0:10:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,點心店都關門了 只好買便利商店的蛋糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.99,0:10:11.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過 生日禮物已經準備好了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.02,0:10:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.68,0:10:15.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.54,0:10:18.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天收拾行李的時候不小心看到了 被我打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽沒藏好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.06,0:10:24.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的好高興 謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.73,0:10:29.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尺寸剛剛好 一高興就走路去兒童森林公園了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.95,0:10:31.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走那麼遠？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.45,0:10:37.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 稍微有點熱 風很舒服 景色也很好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.63,0:10:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還讀了小時候的書
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樹葉在夕陽下閃閃發光好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.56,0:10:43.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.28,0:10:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,媽媽也是為了讓我趕上而買來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天真的是好快樂的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.01,0:11:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你 可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生日快樂 可可娜
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.66,0:11:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.01,0:11:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我們吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.53,0:11:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,充滿愛情的蛋糕終於好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.34,0:11:25.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇 都這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.54,0:11:26.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,得趕緊睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.24,0:11:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們再一起來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.74,0:11:38.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說好了 絕對喔！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.66,0:11:43.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…但是 諾言實現之後又會如何呢
